#summary This is the Example 1 using the Java API

= Identify all human proteins using the Java API =

The Java Code for this example is [http://jbiowh.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/src/main/java/org/jbiowh/tools/examples/FindALLHumProt.java here]

Go to a CMD Windows console or a linux console to execute the java code:

<code language="bash">
java -cp <path-to the-jbiowh-jar-file> org.jbiowh.tools.examples.FindALLHumProt
</code>

The obtained proteins number is the same that the obtained with the others methods.
